The first week of this new year has been blissful practicing with @shivarea108 @kukuiula and sharing beautiful Kauai with her. When I began my practice many years ago at 18, I was also beginning the path in my surfing career both a parallel journey in discovering my inner power and expression. Yoga has always been along side of my surfing to guide me and keep me in my journey in balance and harmony even if things around me were full of many variables.  Towards the end of my professional surfing career I began to recognize this deeper passion for finding flow in my practice and balance in my life after so much traveling, surfing hard and strong for many years in my Yang and wanted to find the yin and more grounding. Taking all I had experienced and learned with my on this new journey I discovered Shiva Rea. She became my new mentor on my path to flow and balance as I began a new chapter in teaching surfing, yoga, wellness w retreat @surfintoyoga. Fast forward to @wonderluust  North Shore Oahu where I taught my largest class and had the honor of first meeting Shiva in person. Fast forward to today on Kauai experiencing a whole week with her has pulled me into a deeper state of flow and balance bringing a whole new love and awakening in my journey of balance and flow. Mahalo nui loa @shivarea108 @siennazenrebel @kukuiula for providing the space and opportunity to start our journey in 2023 🙏🏼🤍🌈✨💜
#shivarae #kukuiula #yogaforsurfers #surfintoyoga #kauaisurfretreats

Cool experience at Waimea Bay today supporting the women surfing in the #redbullmagnitude event @redbullsurfing  @meganabubo and I swam through the shore break and hopped on one of our safety skis to take a closer look and cheer the women on as they road some beautiful waves at the bay.  So stoked to have Megs on the judging panel for Magnitude. She’s a legend and one of my long time  besties

It’s been more than 20 years let’s just say…since I dropped in at Waimea Bay. I went over for the @redbullsurfing #redbullmagnitude to watch the Wahine charge at Waimea. Megs and I swam out through the shore break and jumped on one of the safety skis with @andrewlogreco  to watch and charger them on!  One of my good friends @pomaihoapili paddled out on his 10’4” gave me a big hug and smile and said “let’s go!” I was comfortably sitting and watching  with @meganabubo 
I felt calm and clear and good in my heart as I thought about paddling out, so I did! So happy I listened to my heart and went with the flow of the moment!  Mahalo Pomai for your aloha and @redbullsurfing for supporting the Wahine big wave riders in surfing! 
I would have never thought about paddling out had it not been for all of these elements coming together!  My generation was a different environment than today and I am so happy and grateful to see all of the support and collective coming together to push women surfing to higher levels. This winter has been a magical experience and continues in all levels from big wave riding to @moana.17 getting the wave of her life at the Backdoor shoot out! Then the @theeddieaikau for the first time has women invited and run in a huge swell and the Wahine again are charging! And rising to the occasion! So cool it’s all stepping up to great levels of performance! Tonight @stephaniegilmore is also being awarded for a historic record breaking 8 world titles! So amazing! Go Wahine! It’s about time…
🏆🏄

Last night I had the best dream. @sunnygarcia walked through the door with his big smile and started telling me one of his funny stories laughing. The next part of the dream went into us packing up and headed for the airport to go on a surf trip. We were sitting in the airport hanging out and waiting for our flight when the guy next to us looked at me and said is that Sunny Garcia? I looked over at Sunny and realized he was completely coherent and functioning as his normal healthy self. I woke up and smiled realizing even though it was a dream how real it felt and how lucky I’ve been to experience such a great friend, travel buddy, surf partner, inspiration, and good friend!  Miss surfing with you my friend🫶 
This was from one of many surf experiences we have had together! Championing surfing and living the dream…
